title: Need
lyrics:

[Romanization]

Help me
Baby I’m suffocatin’

Drowning
Deep inside your game

Everytime you come around
Your attention’s what’s all about for me

I’m doing fine, I’m okay

Get away from me

Oh, Oh, Oh
Somebody Help
Cause I can’t wait for anybody else

Oh, Oh, Oh
Somebody Help
Cause I can’t wait
I can’t wait, no

Wanna make up with you
That’s all I want
Pack of cigarette,
Smoked that shit out of the blunt
Sky’s still grey today
Bought an extra pack of cigarette for you, just in case

I - I don’t know
Am I out of my mind? I don’t know
I’m doing fine, I’m okay
I’m doing fine, I’m okay
Yeah

Oh, Oh, Oh
Somebody Help
Cause I, I don’t have nobody else

I’ve been searching through whole city

Can’t wait for anybody else
